<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style='text-align:center'><b><span style='font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">Sri Lanka</span></b><b><span style='font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black'
lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">: Legal Research
and Legal System</span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style='text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style='text-align:center'><i><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">By Aquinas
V. Tambimuttu</span></i></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style='text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style='text-align:justify'><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><a
href="mailto:%3catambimuttu@gmail.com%3e,"><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;text-decoration:none'>Aquinas V. Tambimuttu</span></a></span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black'
lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">,
</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">a
native of Sri Lanka, has an <span style='color:black'>M.L.I.S. from San Jose State University, San Jose, California, an M.A. in English from Santa Clara University, Santa Clara, California, and a B.A. in English from the University of San Francisco.Â  A recent Library and Information Science graduate, Tambimuttu has worked in
Public Services for many years at the Heafey Law Library, at Santa Clara University, as well as at Stanford University Libraries.</span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
color:black' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">Published
January 2009<br />
<a href="Sri_Lanka1.html"><span
style='text-decoration:none'>Read the Update!</span></a></span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style='text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></b></p>
