</span></span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">The
Code of Civil Procedure:Â  Civil Procedure Code. Act 79 of 1988. Amended by Acts
9 of 1991 and 34 of 2000. </span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style='margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;
text-indent:-36.0pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">iii.<span
