</span></span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">Commercial
Code.</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style='margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;
text-indent:-36.0pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">iv.<span
