</span></span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;'>Criminal
Code: Penal Code. Chapter 25. </span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;' lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US">Amended by Penal Code (amendment) Act of 1995.</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style='margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;
